---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- open source PaaS
- brings Pivotal Application Service and Pivotal Container Service

Iaas agnostic!
- Cloud Foundry can be installed on AWS, OpenStack, Google Cloud, Azure, vSphere

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pivotal Application Service (PAS) Features
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Router - routes incoming traffic to the appropriate component
- Authentication - OAuth2, identity management
- Cloud controller - managing the life cycle of applications
- Monitoring, Logging and statistics
- Garden/Diego Cells - manages application instances
- Blob store - Resources, application code, build packs, and droplets
- Service brokers - providing service instances
- Message bus - NATS: publish-subscribe and distributed queueing messaging system

DevOps
- Fully automated deployment, updates
- one-click horizontal and vertical scaling
- Web console

Built in services
- load balancing
- DNS
- automated health management

Automatic Application binding and service provisioning for Pivotal services
- RabbitMQ
- Redis
- Cloud Cache (based on GemFire)
- MySQL


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pivotal Container Service (PKS)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- based on Kubernetes